Package: php-pulsar-client
Version: 2.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: chinakeyboardman
Depends: apache-pulsar-client (>= 2.8.1)
Description: Apache Pulsar client extension for PHP
 Native PHP extension providing bindings to the Apache Pulsar C++ client.
 Supports producers, consumers, readers, TLS, batching, and compression.
